        "Title": "Kleptomaniac Guards",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ANCESTRAL_BULLDOG",
        "PublicId": "128244620678",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository e1f31b51-3e35-48b8-9a68-a73db7e26ed3).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47, your targets are Samuel Simpson, Isaac King, and Harvey Wells, three private security guards known in the criminal underworld to frequently steal the possesions of their employers. Our client, who lost millions due to them, would like their spree put to an end once and for all. They would like you to infiltrate the premises that they are currently working at, maintain cover, and eliminate them, preferably in a manner that appears accidental to avoid suspicion. Good luck 47.",
